clink bundles a derivative of tracking-rule data from the ClearURLs project.

ClearURLs
  Source: https://gitlab.com/ClearURLs/Rules
  Docs:   https://docs.clearurls.xyz
  Licence: GNU Lesser General Public License, version 3.0 (LGPL-3.0)
          https://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl-3.0.txt

The translated snapshot is committed at src/builtin_patterns.toml and
embedded in every clink binary. Run `clink update` to fetch the current
ClearURLs rules into a user-local cache that overrides the bundled snapshot.
